wsj_1128.short-abs-bracketed

    [The Fuji apple may one day replace the Red Delicious as the number one 
U.S. apple.]1   [Since the Red Delicious has been over-planted]2 [and prices
have dropped to new lows,]3  [the apple industry seems ready for change.]4 
[Along with growers, supermarkets are also trying different varieties of
apples.]5  [Although the Fuji is smaller and not as perfectly shaped as the Red
Delicious,]6  [it is much sweeter,less mealy]7  [and has a longer shelf
life.]8 


